text: Moominiiniy Yallak meesittak sin Rabbi Nabii Mucammadal Azali oobisem macaay keenik iyyan waqdi Yalli kayrii kee tirto kaal oobise iyyan, addunyal Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummayseeh meqe taamoomi abbaasite mari teetil meqe mano-le, usun akeer√¢ dabqil addunyal keenih tontocowwimeemik taysem-lon, akeeral Yallak meesita marih dabqi manxu meqe dabqiiy (jannat kinnuk)
